long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: In case you long for the days of the old Trump-Pence logo, this Chrome Extension brings it back.  It replaces images that reference "Trump" or "Pence" with the original Trump-Pence logo.
